@startuml
left to right direction

node "Student Web App" as WebApp
node "API Gateway" as Gateway

node "Listening Microservice" as Service {
    component "ListeningController" as Controller
    component "AntiCheatModule" as AntiCheat
    component "ListeningService" as LService
    component "ScoringEngine" as Scoring
}

node "Auth Service" as Auth
node "Listening DB" as DB
node "Audio Storage\n(Object Storage)" as Storage
node "KPI / Analytics\nService" as Analytics

WebApp <--> Gateway : HTTPS / REST
Gateway --> Controller : REST API

Controller ..> LService
LService ..> AntiCheat
LService ..> Scoring

Service <--> DB : JDBC / SQL
Service --> Analytics : REST
Service --> Storage : HTTP / S3 API
Service <-- Auth : OAuth / JWT

@enduml
